# Python Projects

This folder contains **all Python projects** I have built, organized by complexity.

## Basic Projects
- Mini-projects to practice Python fundamentals.
- Folder: `basic-projects/`
- Projects include:
  - Calculator
  - Even Odd Finder
  - Multiplication Table Generator
  - Number Guessing Game
  - Contact Book
  - Quiz Game
  - Math Toolkit

## Advanced Projects
- More complex applications demonstrating applied Python skills.
- Folder: `advanced-projects/`
- Projects include:
  - Bilingual Translator
  - Book Recommender
  - Movie Recommender
  - Book Finder
  - Weather Data Fetcher
